{"type": "article", "id": 16291, "title": "无线充电面板", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-20T06:30:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125502YsWLwAzIU7QHMjpn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t杜邦™建筑公司与 Power Matters Alliance（无线充电联盟，简称 PMA）合作，推出这款融入无线充电技术的可丽耐® 面板。利用电感耦合在两个面板之间的非接触式感应充电，只需把手机放在特殊标明的可丽耐®面板上，无需插线，就能实现充电。如果这项技术得到推广，那么公共空间如机场、餐厅等地的充电问题就能得到解决。<a href=\"http://www.dupont.co.uk/bi/charging-surfaces/home.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143632yEeDrWL4fTh97AM8.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1077\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.31662592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143633QlJHKGEI2FcnM97S.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143633yaXiOqfTz5w4Ev78.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143634OC6PIgAbiJtaGu9e.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}